{"id":127803,"date":"2022-10-03T17:18:14","date_gmt":"2022-10-03T17:18:14","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/?p=127803"},"modified":"2022-10-03T17:18:14","modified_gmt":"2022-10-03T17:18:14","slug":"scam-alert-mining-global-crypto-added-to-warning-list","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/2022\/10\/03\/scam-alert-mining-global-crypto-added-to-warning-list\/","title":{"rendered":"Scam ALERT: Mining Global Crypto Added to Warning List","gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"text"}]},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Concerned traders have notified the Financial Commission regarding the company<\/span> <a href=\"https:\/\/miningglobalcrypto.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Mining Global Crypto<\/a> (Mining Global Crypto LTD)<b>\u00a0<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">and its associated website.\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone  wp-image-127804\" src=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Untitled-1-copy-300x215.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"215\" height=\"154\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Untitled-1-copy-300x215.png 300w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Untitled-1-copy-230x165.png 230w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Untitled-1-copy-350x250.png 350w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Untitled-1-copy-480x344.png 480w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Untitled-1-copy.png 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 215px) 100vw, 215px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Upon reviewing the submitted information from potential customers of this broker, the Financial Commission has determined that the indicated company and associated website may be used to scam and defraud traders and investors. As such, the Commission does not recommend doing business with this entity, either individuals purporting to represent this broker on social media and in private messages on popular messaging apps. Given this information, <a href=\"https:\/\/miningglobalcrypto.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Mining Global Crypto<\/a> (Mining Global Crypto LTD) will be<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0placed on the Financial Commission\u2019s <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/warning-list\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Warning List<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Don\u2019t miss the latest news and discussion on our Telegram channel. <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/t.me\/Financialcommission\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Subscribe today<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false,"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"html"}]},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Concerned traders have notified the Financial Commission regarding the company Mining Global Crypto (Mining Global Crypto LTD)\u00a0and its associated website.\u00a0\u00a0 &nbsp; &nbsp; Upon reviewing the submitted information from potential customers of this broker, the Financial Commission has determined that the indicated company and associated website may be used to scam and defraud traders and investors. [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false,"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"html"}]},"author":2,"featured_media":102112,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[6614],"tags":[55,56,57,58,59,60,61,62,63,64,65,66,67,68,70,74,6844,6843],"class_list":["post-127803","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-regulatory-actions","tag-brokers","tag-compensationfund","tag-disputeresolution"